ven the design of LRS2,\nincluding systematically studying the spatially resolved properties of extended\nLyman-alpha blobs at 2 < z < 3. LRS2 will provide a powerful spectroscopic\nfollow-up platform for large surveys such as HETDEX.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jul 2014 20:01:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
