ted spanning subgraph with the same $2$-blocks in a strongly connected\ngraph $G$. We present approximation algorithms for three versions of this\nproblem, depending on the type of $2$-blocks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Jul 2014 11:20:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-24"}
