ield strength, this method can be a powerful tool to probe magnetic\nfield decay in neutron stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Jul 2014 15:38:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Aug 2014 11:42:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-30"}
